description:
Mexico was released on August 28th in 1972 and was one of the Les Humphries Singers' biggest hits. It reached number 2 in the German charts and number 1 in Austria and Switzerland.
This performance is from the legendary German TV show Disco.

Remember to subscribe to the channel to stay up-to-date with the latest releases.
https://bit.ly/2MH7erA
#LesHumphriesSingers
